import React from 'react';

import {
  Container,
  ServiceContainer,
  Title,
  FooterItem,
  InstitutionalContainer,
  SocialContainer,
  DownloadsContainer,
  LineContainer,
  ItemText,
} from './styles';

const Footer: React.FC = () => {
  return (
    <Container>
      <ServiceContainer>
        <Title>Services</Title>
        <FooterItem>
          <ItemText />
        </FooterItem>
      </ServiceContainer>
      <InstitutionalContainer>
        <Title>Institutional</Title>
        <FooterItem>
          <ItemText />
        </FooterItem>
      </InstitutionalContainer>
      <SocialContainer>
        <Title>Social Networks</Title>
      </SocialContainer>
      <DownloadsContainer>
        <Title>Downloads</Title>
      </DownloadsContainer>
      <LineContainer />
    </Container>
  );
};

export default Footer;
